snippet.title: Frustrain Teaser
snippet.description:
Few passengers caught vigil in a night train. Sitting in their compartments, submerged into thinking they watch snowflakes flickering behind the window, drink hot brewed tea. And in the corridor looking for a chatmate there walks a man having an odd and scary gift of sociability.

Frustrain – is a surrealistic first-person thriller about some bizarre railroad incident.
